517
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:22,200
<i>Because Kita and I are alike, maybe.</i>

518
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,760
We feel safe to be with one another.

519
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:25,560
<i>Then I must be like that too,</i>

520
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:27,840
<i>because I feel calmer</i>

